  <thing-type id="leviton_dzr15_00_000" listed="false">
    <label>DZR15 Scene Capable Receptacle</label>
    <description>Scene Capable Receptacle&lt;br /&gt&lt;h1&gtOverview&lt;/h1&gt&lt;p&gtZ-Wave Enabled 15 Amp Scene Capable Receptacle with LED Locator - White/Light Almond&lt;/p&gt &lt;p&gtThe wireless Leviton DZR15 is a Z-Wave enabled 15A tamper resistant receptacle designed for use for most residential lighting and motor applications. A large range of load types are supported including incandescent, halogen and magnetic low voltage, electronic low voltage, fluorescent, and motor loads up to Â½ horse power.&lt;/p&gt &lt;br /&gt&lt;h2&gtInclusion Information&lt;/h2&gt&lt;p&gtPress and hold the button on the outlet for 7 seconds until the light starts blinking amber.&lt;/p&gt</description>
